                                               <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A relation between two distinct material entities, the new entity and the old entity, in which the new entity begins to exist through the separation or transformation of a part of the old entity, and the new entity inherits a significant portion of the matter belonging to that part of the old entity."@en ;
