                                            rdfs:subPropertyOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002596> ;
                                            <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "Holds between c and p if and only if c is capable of some activity a, and a negatively regulates p." ;
