                                            <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "The entity A has an activity that directly positively regulates the quantity of B." ;
                                            <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000117> <https://orcid.org/0000-0003-4639-4431> ;
                                            rdfs:label "directly positively regulates quantity of" .


