###  http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0012009
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0012009> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                            rdfs:subPropertyOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002304> ;
                                            <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "p is constitutively upstream of q iff p is causally upstream of q, p is required for execution of q or a part of q, and the execution of p is approximately constant." ;
