<https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000037> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty .


###  https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000038
<https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000038> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty .


