###  http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/GainOfSpecificallyDependentContinuant
<http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/GainOfSpecificallyDependentContinuant> rdf:type owl:Class ;
