###  https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000004
<https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000004> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                       rdfs:subClassOf <https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000015> ,
                                                       [ owl:intersectionOf ( <https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000015>
                                                                              [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0000091> ;
                                                                                owl:someValuesFrom <https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000090>
                                                                              ]
                                                                            ) ;
                                                         rdf:type owl:Class
                                                       ] ;
                                       rdfs:comment """Here, the term “food” is used genuinely in a broad and over-comprehensive sense. 
To delve more into the meanings of “food”, we refer to Borghini et al. (2021) and Borghini and Piras (2020,2021).


Borghini, A., Piras, N., & Serini, B. (2021). From philosophy to ontology: Rethinking food concepts. In CEUR Workshop Proceedings. JOWO Joint Ontology Workshops Episode VII. CEUR-WS. https://air.unimi.it/retrieve/handle/2434/897444/1953096/paper6-IFOW.pdf

Borghini, A., & Piras, N. (2020). Food and Foods. Toward a Definition. Rivista Italiana Di Filosofia Del Linguaggio. https://doi.org/10.4396/SFL2019ES06

Borghini, Andrea, & Piras, N. (2021). On Interpreting Something as Food. Food Ethics, 6(1), 1. https://doi.org/10.1007/s41055-020-00082-5"""@en ;
                                       rdfs:label "food system"@en ;
                                       <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A complex system that pertains to food, to some extent."@en ;
                                       <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000018
<https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000018> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                       rdfs:subClassOf <https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000012> ,
                                                       [ owl:intersectionOf ( <https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000012>
                                                                              [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000178> ;
                                                                                owl:someValuesFrom <https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000031>
                                                                              ]
                                                                              [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002163> ;
                                                                                owl:someValuesFrom <https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000004>
                                                                              ]
                                                                              [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002163> ;
                                                                                owl:allValuesFrom <https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000004>
                                                                              ]
                                                                            ) ;
                                                         rdf:type owl:Class
                                                       ] ;
                                       rdfs:label "food system environment"@en ;
                                       <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A complex system environment that surrounds and is distinct and disjoint from a food system."@en ;
                                       <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000022
