                                       <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000023
<https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000023> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                       rdfs:subClassOf <https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000032> ;
                                       rdfs:label "food system spatial region"@en ;
                                       <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A complex system spatial region of a food system."@en ;
                                       <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000024
<https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000024> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                       owl:equivalentClass [ owl:intersectionOf ( <https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000028>
                                                                                  [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                    owl:onProperty <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000176> ;
                                                                                    owl:someValuesFrom <https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000004>
                                                                                  ]
                                                                                ) ;
                                                             rdf:type owl:Class
                                                           ] ;
                                       rdfs:subClassOf <https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000028> ;
                                       rdfs:comment """Currently, SuMSO refers to food systems as covering different components. Following SCO, meat system components present perspectives.
Nevertheless, we may want to restrict perspectives to living beings.
A possible option may be the exclusion of the following axioms, in order to remove the necessary condition of having a perspective from “food systems component” class.

'system component' and ('has disposition' some perspective) 

'system component' and ('is carrier of' some 'perspective information content entity') 

we refrain from proceeding as such, choosing solely to not establish corresponding \"perspective\" classes for food system components which are generally recognized as non-living entities. We envision discussions with subject matter experts."""@en ;
                                       rdfs:label "food system component"@en ;
                                       <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A complex system component that belongs to a food system."@en ;
                                       <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


###  https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000025
<https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000025> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                       owl:equivalentClass [ owl:intersectionOf ( <https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000024>
                                                                                  [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
                                                                                    owl:onProperty <https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000038> ;
                                                                                    owl:someValuesFrom [ rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                                                                         owl:unionOf ( <https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000027>
                                                                                                                       <https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000029>
                                                                                                                     )
                                                                                                       ]
                                                                                  ]
                                                                                ) ;
                                                             rdf:type owl:Class
                                                           ] ;
                                       rdfs:subClassOf <https://www.w3id.org/sco#SCO_0000034> ;
                                       rdfs:label "food system agent"@en ;
                                       <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A food system component that is an agent in an interaction among food system components or in an interaction between food system components and food system environment components."@en ;
                                       <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


