###  https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000036
<https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000036> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                       owl:equivalentClass [ owl:intersectionOf ( [ rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                                                    owl:unionOf ( <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0000245>
