                                       rdfs:comment "A possible generic “complex system actor” class can be added as necessary."@en ,
                                                    "SuMSO refers to this term in its broad sense, indicating any organism or organization that participate in food supply chain activities. This, however, does not mean that actors have an active role in the activities in which they participate. For discussion on agency in activities see comments under the “complex system activity” class."@en ;
                                       rdfs:label "food system actor"@en ;
                                       rdfs:seeAlso "https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/Core/Supplier" ;
                                       <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "An organism or organization that participates in a food supply chain activity."@en ;
                                       <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Released> .


