###  https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000065
<https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000065> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                       rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000023> ,
