###  https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000097
<https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000097> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                       owl:equivalentClass [ owl:intersectionOf ( <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_9606>
                                                                                  [ rdf:type owl:Restriction ;
