                                                           ] ;
                                       rdfs:subClassOf <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_9606> ;
                                       rdfs:comment "SuMSO currently limits this term to refer to humans. Future implementations will deal with considering machines as workers, for instance, to substitute humans in participating in supply chain activities."@en ,
                                                    "We started to create classes and axioms for some meat supply chain workers. Additional ones are required to complete this hierarchy. We opted to start with those that the stakeholders of our project suggest as the most relevant."@en ;
