###  https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000144
<https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000144> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                       rdfs:subClassOf <https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000063> ;
                                       rdfs:comment """We envision improving this definition and those of the subclasses we created to encompass references to legal reasons and values established and generated through the constitution of the company and its exercise.

This class and related subclasses also require axiomatizations to cover references to information content entities related to company commitment. We envision creating new information content entity classes for this scope."""@en ;
                                       rdfs:label "company-role"@en ;
                                       <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A role that is bearered by a company."@en ;
                                       <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/maturity> <https://spec.industrialontologies.org/ontology/core/meta/AnnotationVocabulary/Provisional> .


###  https://w3id.org/sumso#SuMSO_0000146
